          <p>Use the Business Analyst mobile app when you're out and about to access a large collection of datasets including population, income, housing and consumer behavior. When you're back in the office, you can sync up to the Business Analyst web app.</p>

          <p>
             With the Business Analyst Mobile app, you can:<ul>
			 <li>Get quick demographic and market snapshots.
			 <li>Compare demographic and market data for locations side by side and determine which is suitable for your target market.
			 <li>Take a look at the competition.
			 <li>Set criteria and find out how your location matches up.
			 </ul>
          </p>

