		<p>Business Analyst mobile app requires an account that is part of an ArcGIS Online organization and is a member of a group with access to the Business Analyst application.</p>
		<p>The Business Analyst mobile app supports:<ul>
		 <li>iOs 8.x and 9.x for iPhones and iPads. 7.x is no longer supported.</li>
